<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 13 at 5:55AM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...Some Black Ice This Morning...
Lingering moisture that accumulated onto the roads has frozen this
morning as temperatures have dropped into the upper 20s. Drivers
should be alert to some slick spots on area roads. Black ice is
often hard to see, so drive with extra caution this morning.</description>
